\N<Auntie>Hehe, welcome. This is Auntie's house. And also,
it's your house during summer vacation, Boku-kun.

\N<Boku>My house? Wow! This is amazing! It's my first time
living in such a big house!

\N<Auntie>Hehe, that's right. This house is called a
pension, and many guests come to stay here, so it's a big
house.

\N<Boku>Oh, really? It's interesting to have a house where
lots of people come to stay.
I obtained the super debugging item!

\N<\N[2]>Well then, Harumi-chan. I'm sorry, but could you
please take me to the foot of the mountain? My father will
come to pick me up in the town at the foot.

\N<Art School Onee-chan>Don't worry, I actually have some
business in the town at the foot of the mountain too. So,
how about we go together by bus, Boku-kun?

\N<\N[2]>Sacchan... \N[3] is going back to the city. Today
is our farewell.

\N<Sacchan>Eh... No way... I don't want you to go
somewhere...

[Boku]: Sacchan, you shouldn't be selfish... [Art School
Onee-chan] will have a harder time going back home...

\N<Boku>Sacchan! I will definitely come back! So please
wait for me!

[Art School Onee-chan]: You're amazing, Sacchan. Well,
since the bus is about to arrive, let's say our goodbyes...

Art School \N<Onee-chan>Well, see you later, Boku-kun. Um,
next time, I'll prepare some books that you might like...

\N<Shop Girl>Next time you come, make sure to save up more
pocket money. Contribute to the store's sales.

\N<Aunt>Please come and visit again. Be good friends with
Maa-kun, okay?

\N<Mika-chan>Next time, don't lose to the grass sliding.
Just wash your neck and wait, okay?

\N<Nana-chan>Make sure to come next year too. If you don't
come, there will be punishment, okay?
\N<Boku>I wanted to say goodbye to everyone too...

\N<Art School Onee-chan>Well, since the bus is about to
arrive, shall we go soon?

\N<Boku>Everyone! I thought I wouldn't be able to see you
anymore!

\N<Hakase-kun>It's Boss-kun's fault. Suddenly yesterday, he
said we should all go search...

\N<Boushi-kun>Ah... I'm so exhausted... I've been searching
all this time...

Yuko-kun: It was really tough... But I never expected that
we would actually find it...

\N<Boku>Huh? What? Were you all searching for the
Tsuchinoko together?
\N<Boss-kun>Idiot. It's not like that. This is it, this.

\N<Boku>Eh?! This is a Golden Stag Beetle?! It really
exists?! Amazing!!

\N<Boss-kun>I was thinking of giving something to Boku-chan
before they return to the city. The defense team boys have
been searching for it since yesterday.

\N<Boku>Eh?! You're giving it to me?! Is it really okay to
have something this amazing?!

\N<Boss-kun>Yeah, of course. That is the proof of our
friendship. The Hime-no-yama Defense Team will be forever
immortal!

\N<Boku>Thank you! Boss-kun, Hakase-kun, Boushi-kun, Yuko-
kun! I will treasure it!

\N<Boss-kun>We will hold the Bug Battle Tournament again
next year! The members of the Hime-no-yama Defense Team must
definitely participate!

\N<Hakase-kun>Next year, I will definitely prepare even
more amazing bugs, so be prepared.

\N<Boushi-kun>Next time you come, let's go fishing
together. I know a secret fishing spot!

\N<Yuki-kun>Let's play again sometime. I'll also send you a
letter. It would make me happy if you could reply, even if
it's just occasionally.

\N<\N[2]>Take care and stay well, Boku-kun. Come back here
anytime. This place is already your second home, and we're
like a family, you know.

\N<Onee-chan>We said it on the day we first met here,
right? That it would definitely be a fun summer vacation...
I wonder how it turned out?
\# It was the best summer vacation!

\#The endless blue sky that stretches on and \#the
overwhelming scent of the trees... \#The never-ending sound
of cicadas...

\#I will never forget. \#Those irreplaceable \#distant,
summer days...

\#And so, my summer came to an end. \#But it feels like I
left something important behind. \#That's how my summer
vacation was...
Do you want to skip the ending?
\#A End\# You did a great job!
\#C End\# Let's try a little harder.

\# All Scene Unlock System Unlocked! ※ With the crystals
added to the Secret Picture Diary, it is now possible to
unlock all scenes.

\# Custom Mode Unlocked! ※ You can now access the Secret
Attic Room from the ladder in the storage room on the
second floor of the pension. It is now possible to customize
the appearance of the main characters.

\# Strong and New Game Unlocked! ※ You can now start a new
game while carrying over current bug status, some items, and
some sexual knowledge.

\# Endless Mode Unlocked! ※ This is a mode where you can
continue your summer vacation until August 9999. The
limited-time characters have returned to town, but limited-
time events and new events will not occur.
